************
Compilation
************
from rogue directory
"make"

***********************
Usage
***********************
./run (data file path)
example: "./run ./randLevels.txt"

***********************
Testing
***********************
(after compiling)
"./run ./assets/testFiles/custom.txt”
or "make test"

*****************
Known Limitations
*****************
-data file cannot contain spaces at the end of a line for error checking reasons
-monsters do not move when they run into a wall they skip a cycle

*****************
References
*****************
